      <title>Damage Calculation code bug with backstab.</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Rogue&amp;message.id=4389#M4389</link>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;This is a very obscure bug that would only effect high end rogues, and im not sure if it extends to other classes abilities. As it is right now, if your piercer goes over 32 dmg the dagger will automatically backstab for minimum damage. I started to notice some unusual activity when I looted an &lt;a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=46768" target="_blank"&gt;Etched Obsidian Shard&lt;/a&gt;. I put it in my 2.5 with a verdent emerald of wounding to make, this 32 + 3 / 19&amp;nbsp; dagger. The +3 was elemental of course, but I was consistantly being on the low end of parses and figured it was RNG or me being pre-occupied paying attention to&amp;nbsp; other things while leading raids. When I looted,&amp;nbsp; &lt;a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=46927" target="_blank"&gt;Embershank, The malady&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp; tonight I equipped it and went to go do a weaponry trial to Ooh and Ahhh! So I noticed my attack around 3100, and noticed not most but, EVERY SINGLE backstab was minimum Damage. At first I was like, well this is a fluke. So me and my friends go to a nest mission so I can do some further parsing. Here is the data i found, I first ran&amp;nbsp; through with Embershank and then Jagged Timeforged Blade.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Embershank, The Malady Aug'd with Etched Obsidian Shard to make this dagger 35+1/21.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Backstab:&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;total damage 102,255&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Damage Per Second: 81.28&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Average Hit: 355.05&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Minimum hit 322&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Jagged Timeforged Blade Unaug'd. 20/19&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Backstab:&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Total Damage:&amp;nbsp; 229,586&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Damage Per Second: 251.46&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Average Hit: 922.03&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Minimum Hit: 322&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;From the parse here you can see a plane of time weapon&amp;nbsp; totally dominates&amp;nbsp; a 35+1/21 dagger, the embershank. I'd say its fairly conclusive that there is a bug and im fairly certain the cut off point for this bug is 32dmg as I would only see it on my fully augmented 2.5 dagger when&amp;nbsp; elemental damage hit.&amp;nbsp; This also makes me feel a bit less paranoid, because I thought either A.) Mobs AC went through the roof this expansion, B.) I had the worst luck in the world or C.) I lost my mojo.&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Message Edited by Dalnoth-Vaz on &lt;span class=date_text&gt;12-04-2006&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=time_text&gt;05:58 AM&lt;/span&gt;</description>
